./sdp/logs/Verify_T-009_20260416T043834Z_1776335056.log:14968:Changes include both runtime enforcement and test coverage for the requested behaviors, including event-level voice/sample/grain down-sampling and optional feature suppression. The hardening requirement to invoke `bootstrap_identity()` before first-boot announcement was implemented in both standalone and federated startup paths and test coverage exists. No observed acceptance gaps.
