blem.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n3. Run the relevant tests to confirm the fix and ensure no regressions were introduced.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n4. Commit the change with a clear commit message: `fix(scope): summary [T-021@20260416T181925Z]`\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n## Rules\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n- Do not expand scope; address only the reported problem.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n- Follow existing code style and patterns.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n- Do not clean, revert, commit, or otherwise normalize unrelated pre-existing\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n  workspace changes.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n- Commit your working change immediately.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n## Validation\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nRun this command before finishing:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n```bash\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\npytest tests/ -x --tb=short && ruff check src/ tests/ && mypy src/\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n```\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"}\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n./sdp/logs/Lead_T-021_20260416T181925Z_1776393558.log:48:{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"tool_use\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"timestamp\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"2026-04-17T02:40:12.200Z\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"tool_name\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"run_shell_command\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"tool_id\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"run_shell_command_1776393612200_0\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"parameters\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"com