+  CCS-031 define self-quote capture and end-to-end smoke expectations.
+- Existing behavior already captures a known room descriptor, triggers three
+  fake-JACK self quotes, and finds arc-phase plus acoustic-tag overlap, but
+  `sdp.fractal.classify_depth("my-claw/tools/composer_quote_verify.py")`
