+  CCS-031 define self-quote capture and end-to-end smoke expectations.
+- Existing behavior already captures a known room descriptor, triggers three
+  fake-JACK self quotes, and finds arc-phase plus acoustic-tag overlap, but
+  `sdp.fractal.classify_depth("my-claw/tools/composer_quote_verify.py")`
+  reports depth 1 (`13/18 trivial, 5 real`) because adapter methods dominate
+  the module.
+- Planned depth-2 path: add a stdlib-only typed `QuoteVerificationReport`
+  around the existing end-to-end flow so functions produce reusable diagnostic
+  output while `trigger_composer_pieces`, `find_motif_tag_match`, and CLI
+  success/failure behavior stay compatible.
+- Startup identity hardening is unrelated to this module's capture verifier
