+  the module.
+- Planned depth-2 path: add a stdlib-only typed `QuoteVerificationReport`
+  around the existing end-to-end flow so functions produce reusable diagnostic
+  output while `trigger_composer_pieces`, `find_motif_tag_match`, and CLI
