+## frac-0045 Exploration Findings
+
+- Affected runtime surface: `my-claw/tools/composer_quote_verify.py`, with
+  direct regression coverage in `tests/test_composer_quote_verify.py` and
+  downstream self-listener coverage in `tests/test_self_listener_quote_verify.py`.
+- Related product/architecture context: `docs/cypherclaw-sampler-architecture.md`
